Package: treeExtension
Type: Package
Title: Lightweight Tree Utilities for IQ-TREE Newick Outputs
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Chen", "Yanpeng", email = "yanpengch@qq.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Dependency-free helpers for IQ-TREE Newick strings. Provides
    make_binary_iqtree() to convert an unrooted tree into a rooted binary tree
    by splitting the outgroup pendant branch length equally (L/2 + L/2).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Depends: R (>= 3.5)
Suggests: testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
